    /// # Returns
    ///
    /// * result code for this function.
    /// [`#AUDIOSTREAM_SUCCESS`] succeed in setting to the silent and mix with other streams.
    /// [`#AUDIOSTREAM_ERROR_ILLEGAL_STATE`] this stream is not allowed to set/unset the silent mode.
